2900:Right as we were entering the hospital ward, Rimi ground to a halt.\p;
3000:〔Rimi〕“I need to use the bathroom real quick. You guys go on ahead.”\p;
3100:With a wave of her hand, Rimi quickly headed back toward the outpatient ward.\p;
3200:Thinking that wandering around the ward would cause problems for the patients, we decided to ask for help at the nurses' station. And just like I'd predicted, they told us that she was on the floor for psychiatric patients.\p;
